it.unibz.krdb.obda.owlrefplatform.core.dagjgrapht

Class GabowSCC<V,E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unibz.krdb.obda.owlrefplatform.core.dagjgrapht.GabowSCC<V,E>

  • public class GabowSCC<V,E>
extends Object
    Allows obtaining the strongly connected components of a directed graph. The implemented algorithm follows Cheriyan-Mehlhorn/Gabow's algorithm Presented in Path-based depth-first search for strong and biconnected components by Gabow (2000). The running time is order of O(|V|+|E|) TODO: replace by GabowStrongConnectivityInspector (from an updated JGraphT)
